import math

def find_min_strips(A, B):
    return math.ceil(B / A) if A > 0 and B > 0 else 0

def main():
    A, B = [int(x) for x in input().split()]
    print(find_min_strips(A, B))

if __name__ == '__main__':
    main()

import re

def solution(text):
    text = text.lower()
    text = re.sub(r'[^a-z]', '', text)
    text = re.sub(r'(.)\1+', r'\1', text)
    return text
